================================================================================
Credits & third-party components
================================================================================

The MIT license above covers only obsidianet's own code (the admin panel, the
Docker Compose setup, and the documentation).

The notes application at the heart of obsidianet is **Docmost**, an open-source
Notion/Confluence alternative. obsidianet runs Docmost's official, unmodified
container image; no Docmost source code is redistributed here. All credit for the
notes experience goes to the Docmost project and its contributors.

  Docmost — https://github.com/docmost/docmost
  Licensed under AGPL-3.0 (with an optional Enterprise edition).
  © the Docmost authors.

obsidianet also builds on these open-source projects, each under its own license:

  Next.js      — https://github.com/vercel/next.js            (MIT)
  Recharts     — https://github.com/recharts/recharts          (MIT)
  Caddy        — https://github.com/caddyserver/caddy          (Apache-2.0)
  PostgreSQL   — https://www.postgresql.org                    (PostgreSQL License)
  Redis        — https://github.com/redis/redis                (RSALv2/SSPL/AGPL)
  node-postgres, bcryptjs, jose, Tailwind CSS — MIT

Trademarks and product names are the property of their respective owners.
